    "body": "Thanks for your reply @vvo,\nI want to use it to sort product categories, for example\nClothing\n  Clothing > Dresses\n    Clothing > Mini Dresses\n    Clothing > Midi Dresses\n  Clothing > Tops\n  Clothing > Bottoms\n  Clothing > Outwears\nAccessories\n  Accessories > Jewelery\n  Accessories > Bags\n...\n\nI need to sort items by levels name:desc - count:desc -  or custom sort function for each level.\n",
